Package com.sicomsa.dmt

Class Authorization

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.Authorization
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Authorization extends Object implements Serializable
Authorization contains the token provided from SAT to access massive download web services. Includes instant the authorization was received, created and its expiration.
Since:
1.0
Version:
2024.9.9
